introduction: Crew Kingston Miskel was born in a suburb of Chicago. Following in his brother and sister's footsteps, he found his love for acting, modeling, and sports at an early age. Crew is extremely talented, focused, and mature and is the brightest light in any room. His comedic timing and story telling abilities provide for constant entertainment. Crew was cast in a recurring role on The Big Leap premiering on Fox in 2021 as the adorable Sam Lewis. He also booked roles on Chicago PD and Chicago Med in 2023. In 2024, he filmed his latest recurring role on Emperor of Ocean Park on MGM+. Crew is also the voice of Redbird for Batwheels Season 2 and he loves bringing his character to life. He has also done extensive print and commercial work since the age of 3 months. When Crew isn't on set, he is excelling at basketball, baseball, or football. In 2024, he showed his amazing basketball skills by winning against adults in a basketball shooting competition with a huge cash prize. Crew is an exceptional student and loves to talk college and pro sports to anyone who will listen. He sings, plays piano and spends any free time watching sports or playing video games.
